import React, { useState, useEffect } from 'react'; import { useForm, useFieldArray } from 'react-hook-form'; import { obstetricsService } from '../../services/obstetricsService'; import toast from 'react-hot-toast'; import { Plus, Minus, Save, X } from 'lucide-react'; import Modal from '../common/Modal'; import LoadingSpinner from '../common/LoadingSpinner'; const EditObstetricsCarePlanModal = ({ isOpen, onClose, onSuccess, carePlan }) => { const [loading, setLoading] = useState(false); const [activeTab, setActiveTab] = useState('basic'); const { register, handleSubmit, control, reset, formState: { errors } } = useForm(); const { fields: supplementFields, append: appendSupplement, remove: removeSupplement } = useFieldArray({ control, name: 'careDetails.sleepNutrition.supplements' }); useEffect(() => { if (carePlan && isOpen) { reset({ patientId: carePlan.patientId || '', patientName: carePlan.patientName || '', doctorId: carePlan.doctorId || '', doctorName: carePlan.doctorName || '', careType: carePlan.careType || 'prenatal', gestationalWeek: carePlan.gestationalWeek || '', instructions: carePlan.instructions || '', priority: carePlan.priority || 'medium', status: carePlan.status || 'active', careDetails: { trimesterSymptoms: { nausea: carePlan.careDetails?.trimesterSymptoms?.nausea || 'none', cramps: carePlan.careDetails?.trimesterSymptoms?.cramps || 'none', mood: carePlan.careDetails?.trimesterSymptoms?.mood || 'stable', fatigue: carePlan.careDetails?.trimesterSymptoms?.fatigue || 'none' }, babyMovement: { frequency: carePlan.careDetails?.babyMovement?.frequency || 'normal', notes: carePlan.careDetails?.babyMovement?.notes || '' }, sleepNutrition: { sleepHours: carePlan.careDetails?.sleepNutrition?.sleepHours || 8, sleepQuality: carePlan.careDetails?.sleepNutrition?.sleepQuality || 'good', dietNotes: carePlan.careDetails?.sleepNutrition?.dietNotes || '', waterIntake: carePlan.careDetails?.sleepNutrition?.waterIntake || 2, supplements: carePlan.careDetails?.sleepNutrition?.supplements || [] }, postnatalRecovery: { bleeding: carePlan.careDetails?.postnatalRecovery?.bleeding || 'none', stitchesCondition: carePlan.careDetails?.postnatalRecovery?.stitchesCondition || 'not-applicable', painLevel: carePlan.careDetails?.postnatalRecovery?.painLevel || 0, emotionalState: carePlan.careDetails?.postnatalRecovery?.emotionalState || 'stable' } }, vitalSigns: { bloodPressure: { systolic: carePlan.vitalSigns?.bloodPressure?.systolic || '', diastolic: carePlan.vitalSigns?.bloodPressure?.diastolic || '' }, weight: carePlan.vitalSigns?.weight || '', temperature: carePlan.vitalSigns?.temperature || '', heartRate: carePlan.vitalSigns?.heartRate || '' }, nextAppointment: carePlan.nextAppointment ? new Date(carePlan.nextAppointment).toISOString().slice(0, 16) : '' }); } }, [carePlan, isOpen, reset]); const onSubmit = async (data) => { if (!carePlan) return; setLoading(true); try { const result = await obstetricsService.updateCarePlan(carePlan._id, data); if (result.success) { toast.success('Obstetrics care plan updated successfully'); onSuccess(); } else { toast.error(result.message || 'Failed to update care plan'); } } catch (error) { toast.error('Error updating care plan'); console.error('Error:', error); } finally { setLoading(false); } }; const handleClose = () => { reset(); onClose(); }; const tabs = [ { id: 'basic', label: 'Basic Info' }, { id: 'care', label: 'Care Details' }, { id: 'vitals', label: 'Vital Signs' } ]; return (
{/* Tab Navigation */}
